## Case 2: Revenue Concentration & Portfolio Analysis (Pareto & Regional Dynamics)
**Objective:** Identify key revenue drivers and structural market differences to optimize resource allocation.

### Key Insights
* **Revenue Concentration:** Applied Pareto Analysis (80/20 rule) to identify high-value titles driving the ecosystem's P&L.
* **Geographical Structure:** Visualized regional preference shifts (NA vs JP vs EU) to support localization and regional pricing strategies.

